  <brief_title>Efficacy of Irinotecan and Capecitabine Versus(vs) Cisplatin and Capecitabine in Patients With Esophago-Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Open, Comparative Multicentre Phase II Study for the Evaluation of Irinotecan and Capecitabine Versus Cisplatin and Capecitabine in Advanced Gastric Adenocarcinoma or Gastric-Oesophagal Junction</official_title>
