  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine which Arm (capecitabine + irinotecan versus
      capecitabine + cisplatin) shows higher response rates in the treatment of advanced
      gastric-oesophagal cancer

      Furthermore, comparison of progression-free survival, 1-year survival, Quality of Life and
      safety
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      capecitabine + irinotecan versus capecitabine + cisplatin, as published by Kang et al. (ASCO
      2006)
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
